{"tid":2155675,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Epic Games 大作 Fortnite 於 App Store 全球下架","createTime":"2020-08-14T02:52:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-15T05:34:41.000Z","uid":1121,"like":46,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"a5c5ad4a1eb2a96f175476b65856af5c66a709c8","tid":2155675,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T02:52:17.000Z","msg":"著名 Epic Games 遊戲 Fortnite 今天突然在 App Store 全球下架，原因是 Epic Games 在遊戲裡加入跳過 App Store 內購付費的直接付費功能。<br />\n<br />\nApp Store 的條款中，不容許遊戲使用第三方付費方式，從而透過內購抽取 3 成的佣金費用。今次 Fortnite 加入直接付費功能明顯是觸犯 App Store 的底線。Apple 表示 Epic 該直接付費功能並沒有取得 Apple 的批准。<br />\n<br />\n內購付費跟 Spotify 這類訂閱服務有不同之處，訂閱服務首年收費為 30%，之後會降至 15%。然而內購則會維持 30%。而 Epic Games 也因為 Fortnite 被下架而提出訴訟，反擊 Apple 下架的決定。雖然 Fortnite 被下架，但已下載到 iOS 裝置的 Fortnite 仍可繼續玩。"},{"pid":"ea1db6f6d7ea604362df86622baf7d8f0eee323a","tid":2155675,"uid":1121,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T02:53:17.000Z","msg":"Epic Games源自美國的遊戲公司，<span class=\"red\">在2012年與騰訊達成協議，後者將會收購Epic 40%的股權，成為該公司的大股東之一。<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"fdd9811039f707556c6f2f2ebc6a7300cfdc9773","tid":2155675,"uid":196924,"like":56,"dislike":1,"score":55,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T02:54:22.000Z","msg":"要喺人地個App Store賣, 又唔守人規矩<br />\n4成騰訊果然係唔同啲"},{"pid":"1131199081bc157aade20162533849d71b4ee2c4","tid":2155675,"uid":1121,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"fdd9811039f707556c6f2f2ebc6a7300cfdc9773","tid":2155675,"uid":196924,"like":56,"dislike":1,"score":55,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T02:54:22.000Z","msg":"要喺人地個App Store賣, 又唔守人規矩<br />\n4成騰訊果然係唔同啲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T03:00:29.000Z","msg":"依家風頭火勢仲玩依d，抵比人下架啦"},{"pid":"dd1a5caf181ea9207a0e2cf6ae69563735967b2a","tid":2155675,"uid":61653,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T03:02:21.000Z","msg":"大陸野係咁唔守規矩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"686fbbde4c4f16811c0d03a88b8882efc419db41","tid":2155675,"uid":11148,"l